<HL>
   Corona, Homestake
   Are Negotiating
   A Possible Merger
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/13/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C17
</SO>
<CO>
   DBC.A HM ICR T.ICR
</CO>
